Introduction

DIGNITY is a five-member boy group under PCS Entertainment. They made their official pre-debut on September 23 of 2022 with the digital single "Rambo".

In 2023 the group participated in JTBC's survival show Peak Time but were eliminated in the 2nd round.

They announced their official debut with their first mini album "Digmotion" set to be released on July 24, 2024.
